{"tid":2108304,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"免費送Watch Dogs 2 PC 版","createTime":"2020-07-14T12:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T12:39:48.000Z","uid":235152,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"dcb95d409bb77b51b30dc849a9374ee1fefb5fdf","tid":2108304,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"Ubisoft 宣佈，原本要在 Ubisoft Forward 網上發佈會上實時觀看的觀眾才可免費獲得的 Watch Dogs 2 的 PC 版本，現時只要前往指定網站，填寫好 Uplay 帳號相關資料即可免費獲得。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\nUbisoft 在周日（12 日）舉行 Ubisoft Forward 網上發佈會前，已公佈會向所有實時觀看發佈會的觀眾免費送出遊戲 Watch Dogs 2 的 PC 版本，惟當日人流太多，以致官網和 Uplay 啟動器「塞車」，不少有意觀看直播換上遊戲的玩家因而失望。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n不過，Ubisoft 宣佈，決定將這套作品免費派發，有興趣的玩家只要到指定網站，填寫 Uplay 帳號相關資料，遊戲會在一定時間內出現在其遊戲庫。不過，要留意的是，參加者亦必須年滿 18 歲，且某些地區亦會因法規的問題而無法參與此次活動<br />\n<br />\n登記網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://register.ubisoft.com/ubisoft-forward-reward/en-US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fregister.ubisoft.com%2Fubisoft-forward-reward%2Fen-US&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=7eca7468\" target=\"_blank\">https://register.ubisoft.com/ubisoft-forward-reward/en-US</a>"},{"pid":"a5183d09673f6a026514ec1efa47eb9d0582ab0e","tid":2108304,"uid":92467,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:24:44.000Z","msg":"某些地區亦會因法規的問題而無法參與此次活動<br />\n係咪中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f9e461fd6515d7504d287c1499049ead21125b","tid":2108304,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"502"},{"pid":"0c54f39c042d5391947bd4a4804e48aee9561ac8","tid":2108304,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"拎左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a54612f74d5407dfb48dae4490927694b8fd62f","tid":2108304,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:55:06.000Z","msg":"尋晚登記, 今日仲未收到..<img src=\